summaries.short: After their blackmail case becomes a suspicious death investigation, Strike and Robin piece together a crucial break in the case.
summaries.full: When their blackmail case turns into a suspicious death investigation, Strike and Robin increase their pressure on everyone involved. As Robin goes undercover to infiltrate Jimmy's inner-circle with help from his unsuspecting girlfriend Flick, she finds herself in a dangerous predicament. Meanwhile, Strike and Robin's unshakeable rapport leads to a break in the case.

summaries.short: Season Two Finale. As Strike and Robin close in on the truth, Robin's unanticipated panic attack places them in grave danger.
summaries.full: Season Two Finale. After Robin makes a life-changing decision, she throws herself into the final stretch of the investigation, while Strike contends with a profound declaration of his own. Just as they close in on the truth, Robin's unanticipated panic attack places them--and the future of the case--in grave danger.

summaries.short: As Jimmy increases his blackmail demands against Chiswell, Strike and Robin struggle to stop him.
summaries.full: In the wake of the previous night's startling discovery, Strike begins a frantic search for Billy--but learns he may not be the only one after him. On her anniversary getaway with Matthew, Robin is distracted by more than just the case, and Strike runs into his ex-girlfriend Charlotte, who shares unsettling news.

summaries.short: Season Two Premiere. Just after Billy Knight pays them a visit, Strike and Robin are hired to investigate Billy's brother Jimmy.
summaries.full: Season Two Premiere. An unstable Billy Knight pays a visit to private detective Cormoran Strike and his partner Robin Ellacott, detailing a traumatizing incident he witnessed as a child. Then, minister Jasper Chiswell hires the duo to investigate his blackmailer--Billy's brother Jimmy. As Strike and Robin struggle to connect the cases, they make a devastating discovery.

summaries.short: Season One Finale. As the killer continues to taunt them, Robin and Strike arrive closer to the truth.
summaries.full: Season One Finale. As Strike and Robin search for clues on their three suspects, Robin's mother arrives in London to encourage her to make a decision about the wedding. After visiting with Kelsey's sister, Strike is scolded by an angry DI Wardle for meddling with police business, while Robin questions a suspect's girlfriend.
